data.title: Falling In Reverse & Escape The Fate Announce ‘Bury The Hatchet’ Sidewaves
data.meta_description: Las Vegas outfits Falling In Reverse and Escape The Fate will be joining forces to bring two Bury The Hatchet Sidewaves to Melbourne and Sydney this February, along with with special guests The Color Morale. The hardcore outfits will bring their Bury The Hatchet show to Melbourne’s 170 Russell on Wednesday 25th February, followed by […]
